## Prerequisites & Access

```bash
# Context
export NS=url-shortener-prod
export MONGOS_URI="mongodb://mongos-router.url-shortener.svc.cluster.local:27017/urlsrv"
export REDIS_CLI="redis-cli -c -h redis-cluster.url-shortener.svc.cluster.local -p 6379"

# Kafka
export KAFKA_BROKERS="kafka-0.kafka.url-shortener.svc:9092,kafka-1.kafka.url-shortener.svc:9092"

# CDN Purge
export CDN_API_KEY=<from Vault>
export CDN_PURGE_URL="https://api.cdnprovider.com/v1/purge"
```

